                        Traveler Resources
                     
                 
                Since 1985, Natural Habitat Adventures has aimed to give travelers all kinds of reasons to get excited about exploring. One of the most commonly overlooked joys of traveling is preparing for your trip. From books and clothing offered through our Gear Store, to wildlife webinars and videos to stoke your anticipation, to learning about our carbon offset program and travel protection plans, we've got you covered when it comes to traveler resources! 
                                
                
