                                                \t\t\t\t 
                                                \t\t\t\t
                                                \t\t\t\t\tCarbon Offsets 
                                                \t\t\t\t\t
                                                \t\t\t\t\t\t
                                                \t\t\t\t\t\t\tSince we became the world's first 100-percent carbon-neutral travel company in 2007, all Nat Hab adventures and office operations have been operated in a completely carbon-neutral manner. Beginning in 2019, we are now offsetting all of our guests' flights to and from our destinations! 
  
  
